This repository contains the necessary cookbooks to install and configure Graylog2.

Here are a few options:
  1) Copy these cookbooks into your Chef cookbook repository
  2) Clone this repository to your workstation, an launch Graylog2 in a VM with Vagrant
  3) Clone this repository to your desired server and install graylog2 with chef-solo.


== Contributing

Please contribute updates, additions or documentation changes.


